  <brief_title>Impact of Opportunistic Salpingectomy on Ovarian Reserve in Patients Undergoing Laparoscopic Hysterectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of Opportunistic Salpingectomy on Ovarian Reserve in Patients Undergoing Laparoscopic Hysterectomy: a Multi-center, Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
